'''韓仕新'''<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.bcbudget.gov.bc.ca/2009/highlights/2009_Highlights_Ch.pdf |title=2009年預算案要點 |publisher=卑詩省政府 |accessdate=2020-12-16 |language=zh-hant |archive-date=2018-10-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181029211530/https://www.bcbudget.gov.bc.ca/2009/highlights/2009_Highlights_Ch.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.singtao.ca/4567611/2020-10-25/news-%E3%80%90%E5%8D%91%E8%A9%A9%E7%9C%81%E9%81%B8%E3%80%913%E5%A4%A7%E9%BB%A8%E9%A0%98%E9%80%A3%E4%BB%BB/?variant=zh-hk|title=【卑詩省選】3大黨領連任|publisher=《星島日報》加西版|date=2020-10-25|accessdate=2020-12-16|quote=在韋勤信獲選為該選區省議員之前，該選區是由省自由黨前財政廳長韓仕新(Colin Hansen)擔任省議員。|archive-date=2020-10-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201026010508/https://www.singtao.ca/4567611/2020-10-25/news-%E3%80%90%E5%8D%91%E8%A9%A9%E7%9C%81%E9%81%B8%E3%80%913%E5%A4%A7%E9%BB%A8%E9%A0%98%E9%80%A3%E4%BB%BB/?variant=zh-hk|dead-url=no}}</ref>（{{lang|en|Colin Hansen}}，{{bd|1952年||}}），[[加拿大|加拿大]]政治人物，1996年-2013年間以[[卑詩自由黨|卑詩自由黨]]黨員身份擔任[[卑詩省議會|卑詩省議會]][[溫哥華奎秦拿選區|溫哥華奎秦拿選區]]議員，並曾在前[[卑詩省省長|省長]][[戈登·坎贝尔|金寶爾]]的內閣中出任數項廳長職務，當中包括於2009年-11年間任職[[卑詩省副省長|卑詩省副省長]]，以及兩度擔任該省財政廳長。

==生平==
韓仕新於[[卑詩省|卑詩省]][[艾伯尼港|艾伯尼港]]出生<ref name="CPG"/>，1975年從[[維多利亞大學_(加拿大)|維多利亞大學]]取得政治學文學士學位<ref name="BCGov041214">{{cite web |url=https://archive.news.gov.bc.ca/releases/archive/2001-2005/2004otp0095-001079-attachment1.htm |title=BIOGRAPHIES |publisher=卑詩省政府 |accessdate=2020-12-14 |date=2004-12-14 |archive-date=2020-12-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201221153411/https://archive.news.gov.bc.ca/releases/archive/2001-2005/2004otp0095-001079-attachment1.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他於1983年成為[[亞太基金會|加拿大亞太基金會]]財務及行政副總裁，1988年則與妻子羅拉在[[溫哥華|溫哥華]]創辦促銷產品公司形象集團（{{lang|en|Image Group}}）<ref name="CPG"/><ref name="BCGov041214"/>。

他於1996年省選代表[[卑詩自由黨|卑詩自由黨]]競逐[[溫哥華奎秦拿選區|溫哥華奎秦拿選區]]議席並告當選，首度晉身[[卑詩省議會|省議會]]，並於自由黨在野時期出任官方反對黨[[影子內閣|影子內閣]]的衛生、就業及投資、和勞工評議員<ref name="CPG"/><ref name="BCLeg39">{{cite web |url=https://www.leg.bc.ca/pages/bclass-legacy.aspx#%2Fcontent%2Flegacy%2Fweb%2Fmla%2F39thparl%2Fhansenc.htm |title=39th Parliament Members at dissolution on April 16, 2013: Colin Hansen |publisher=[[卑詩省議會|卑詩省議會]] |accessdate=2020-12-15 |archive-date=2019-08-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190820154630/https://www.leg.bc.ca/pages/bclass-legacy.aspx#%2Fcontent%2Flegacy%2Fweb%2Fmla%2F39thparl%2Fhansenc.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。自由黨於2001年省選大勝[[卑詩新民主黨|新民主黨]]，以多數政府姿態上台執政，連任省議員的韓仕新獲省長[[戈登·坎贝尔|金寶爾]]委入內閣，出任衛生服務廳長<ref name="CPG"/><ref name="BCGov041214"/>。金寶爾於2004年12月調動內閣，韓仕新改任財政廳長<ref name="BCLeg39"/>。

他於2005年省選連任奎秦拿選區省議員，在金寶爾內閣改任經濟發展廳長、專責亞太策略廳長和專責[[2010年冬季奧運會|2010年冬奧]]廳長<ref name="BCLeg39"/>。財政廳長泰萊（{{lang|en|Carole Taylor}}）於2008年請辭後，金寶爾委派韓仕新第二度出任財長<ref name="BCLeg39"/>。2009年省選後，韓仕新在金寶爾內閣留任財長，並兼任副省長<ref name="BCLeg39"/>。他從2010年10月起兼任專責小型企業廳長<ref name="BCLeg39"/>，再從同年11月起兼任衛生服務廳長<ref>{{cite web |url=https://archive.news.gov.bc.ca/releases/news_releases_2009-2013/2010PREM0206-001511.htm |title=Health Services Minister Appoined |publisher=[[卑詩省省長|卑詩省省長]]辦公室 |date=2010-11-30 |accessdate=2020-12-15 |archive-date=2020-12-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201221153412/https://archive.news.gov.bc.ca/releases/news_releases_2009-2013/2010PREM0206-001511.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

自由黨贏取2009年省選後不久，金寶爾和韓仕新於同年7月23日宣佈卑詩省將從2010年7月1日起實行[[合併銷售稅|合併銷售稅]]（HST）<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.cbc.ca/canada/british-columbia/story/2009/07/23/bc-hst-pst-gst.html | work=CBC News | title=B.C. moves to 12 per cent HST | date=July 23, 2009 | accessdate=2020-12-16 | archive-date=2010-02-09 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100209235157/http://www.cbc.ca/canada/british-columbia/story/2009/07/23/bc-hst-pst-gst.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>，把原來的5%聯邦銷售及服務稅和7%省銷售稅合併成一個稅率為12%的[[加拿大銷售稅|統一稅制]]。新稅制旨在簡化商家的行政手續，因此普遍獲商界支持。然而，HST實施後，部分原本無需收取省銷售稅的服務（如理髮和地毯清潔）需改為收取全數12%的銷售稅<ref>{{cite web |last= |first= |url=http://www.ctv.ca/CTVNews/QPeriod/20090723/bc_tax_090723/ |title=B.C. to harmonize provincial sales tax and GST |publisher=Canadian Press, via CTV |date=2009-07-23 |accessdate=2011-02-26 |archive-date=2012-07-29 |archive-url=https://archive.today/20120729033619/http://www.ctv.ca/CTVNews/QPeriod/20090723/bc_tax_090723/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，被部分人指為變相加稅，因此方案也被不少反對派人士<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.bcndp.ca/newsroom/surprise-decision-new-tax-could-kill-tourism-service-jobs |title=Surprise decision on new tax could kill tourism, service jobs | BC NDP |publisher=Bcndp.ca |date= |accessdate=2010-11-29 |archive-date=2012-02-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120218060829/http://www.bcndp.ca/newsroom/surprise-decision-new-tax-could-kill-tourism-service-jobs |dead-url=no }}</ref>以至普通省民大力反對<ref>{{cite web |author=Global BC; Ipsos Reid: Wednesday, August 5, 2009 |url=http://www.globaltvbc.com/Ipsos+Reid+Global+News+Poll/1863303/story.html |title=Ipsos Reid/Global News HST Poll |publisher=Globaltvbc.com |date=2009-08-05 |accessdate=2010-11-29 |archive-date=2012-02-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120229202019/http://www.globaltvbc.com/Ipsos+Reid+Global+News+Poll/1863303/story.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |author=Angus Reid Public Opinion |url=http://www.visioncritical.com/2010/06/referendum-and-recall-drive-loom-as-serious-threats-to-bc-liberals/ |title=Angus Reid Public Opinion |publisher=Vision Critical |date= |accessdate=2010-11-29 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100810205127/http://www.visioncritical.com/2010/06/referendum-and-recall-drive-loom-as-serious-threats-to-bc-liberals/ |archivedate=2010-08-10 }}</ref>。

受HST風波影響，自由黨民望急跌<ref>{{cite news |last=Shaw |first=Rob |url=http://www.timescolonist.com/news/Campbell+popularity+hits+rock+bottom/3681197/story.html |title=Senior B.C. officials discussed the HST before the election, documents reveal |publisher=Times Colonist |date=2010-09-02 |accessdate=2010-11-29 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101121045354/http://www.timescolonist.com/news/Campbell+popularity+hits+rock+bottom/3681197/story.html |archivedate=2010-11-21 }}</ref>，金寶爾遂於2010年11月3日宣佈辭去省長及自由黨黨魁職務<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.mingpaovan.com/htm/News/20101104/vaa1h.htm|title=恐遭「逼宮」 金寶爾下台|publisher=《明報》加西版|date=2010-11-04|first=|last=|accessdate=2011-01-30|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110111072053/http://www.mingpaovan.com/htm/news/20101104/vaa1h.htm|archivedate=2011-01-11}}</ref>。在其後舉行的自由黨黨魁選舉中，韓仕新支持[[馮宜幹|馮宜幹]]<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.straight.com/article-375887/vancouver/significance-colin-hansens-endorsement-bc-liberal-leadership-candidate-kevin-falcon |title=The significance of Colin Hansen's endorsement of B.C. Liberal leadership candidate Kevin Falcon |publisher=''The Georgia Straight'' |first=Charlie |last=Smith |date=2011-02-19 |accessdate=2020-12-16 |archive-date=2011-04-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110427083910/http://www.straight.com/article-375887/vancouver/significance-colin-hansens-endorsement-bc-liberal-leadership-candidate-kevin-falcon |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[簡蕙芝|簡蕙芝]]於2011年當選該黨黨魁並就任省長後，未有委派韓仕新入閣<ref>{{cite web |last=MacLeod |first=Andrew |url=https://thetyee.ca/News/2011/03/15/ChristyClarkCabinet/ |title='Christy Has a Whole New Team' |publisher=The Tyee |date=2011-03-15 |accessdate=2020-12-15 |archive-date=2017-06-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170613110151/https://thetyee.ca/News/2011/03/15/ChristyClarkCabinet/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.ccue.com/ccp_west/2011-03-17/1300390590d3067526.html|title=簡蕙芝就任省長 內閣減人數|publisher=《星島日報》加西版（轉載於事事如意生活網）|date=2011-03-18|accessdate=2020-12-16|archive-date=2020-12-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201221153412/http://www.ccue.com/ccp_west/2011-03-17/1300390590d3067526.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在同年自由黨周年大會中，韓仕新建議該黨更名，以反映其與[[加拿大自由黨|聯邦自由黨]]的政治理念有異，且兩黨互不隸屬<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/british-columbia/b-c-liberals-should-consider-name-change-hansen-1.1032917 |title=B.C. Liberals should consider name change: Hansen |publisher=The Canadian Press, via CBC News |date=2011-05-13 |accessdate=2020-12-16 |archive-date=2020-12-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201221153443/https://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/british-columbia/b-c-liberals-should-consider-name-change-hansen-1.1032917 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

他於2012年9月宣布不會在2013年省選中競逐連任省議員<ref>{{cite web |url=https://ipolitics.ca/2012/09/21/veteran-politician-colin-hansen-bows-out-of-b-c-politics/ |title=Veteran politician Colin Hansen bows out of B.C. politics |publisher=The Canadian Press, via iPolitics |date=2012-09-21 |accessdate=2020-12-15 |archive-date=2012-10-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121031112654/http://www.ipolitics.ca/2012/09/21/veteran-politician-colin-hansen-bows-out-of-b-c-politics/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。離開政壇後，韓仕新從2014年起出任非牟利組織「卑詩優勢」（{{lang|en|AdvantageBC}}）總裁，向國外商戶推廣卑詩省的投資機遇<ref>{{cite web |last=Hyslop |first=Lucy |url=https://www.bcbusiness.ca/colin-hansen-on-vancouvers-future-as-a-yuan-trading-hub |title=Colin Hansen on Vancouver's future as a yuan trading hub |publisher=BC Business |date=2015-02-13 |accessdate=2020-12-16 |archive-date=2020-12-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201221153417/https://www.bcbusiness.ca/colin-hansen-on-vancouvers-future-as-a-yuan-trading-hub |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

